Introduction

Neneko Mashiro is a South Korean V-Tuber and singer under Accelers. She is a member of the South Korean VTuber group StelLive and part of the subunit: 2nd Generation 'Universe'. She debuted as a soloist on October 16, 2024 with the digital single ''Springdream''.

Her birth year is unknown, but the date is known to be February 22.
